          "tz": 60
        },
        "subject": "LDEV-644 utils: always build liblustreapi.la",
        "message": "LDEV-644 utils: always build liblustreapi.la\n\nCommit 7b659a1e68174212c443761be1880774b440a901\n(\"LU-5541 build: move libcfs and liblustreapi over to libtool\")\nhas introduced a regression where liblustreapi.la will not be\nbuilt if configured with \"--disable-utils\" but also that some test\nbinaries linking to this lib are unconditionally built even when\n\"--disable-tests\". This causes build to fail when both\n\"--disable-utils --disable-tests\" are specified, like presently\nduring on-target configure step of lustre-dkms RPM.\n\nThis patch allows liblustreapi.la build even if \"--disable-utils\".\n\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I52ddae9ffddd6e74cb91c3a53360845d896e6bfb\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
